To this day I still benefit from the contacts I have made through the competitions.
The franchise sale of his hotel helped Lukas Pytloun to win the Best Individual Entrepreneur contest.
Last year's winner of the Best Individual Entrepreneur competition was 28-year-old entrepreneur Lukas Pytloun.
His journey to success is like a movie.
Lukas Pytloun was a traveller.
