The aim of this year's Absurdity of the Year contest is to highlight all the regulations and decrees that companies and entrepreneurs have to comply with in the Czech Republic and to have those that are absurd removed.
This survey is again this year for the fourth time part of the business clan organized by Hospodarske noviny and has even greater popularity.
If last year 3,000 voters showed up, at least 4,000 this year have voted.
