The other two dogs from four stolen from outside a motel in Bellflower were found, the Los Angeles County Sheriff's Department announced Thursday.
The four show dogs - two Akitas and two Welsh Pembroke Corgis - went missing on Tuesday when someone stole the Chevrolet Express van they had spent the night in outside a motel 6 in Bellflower, authorities said.
